----------------------------------------------------------------------
				   
			F  I  D  O  G  A  T  E
				 ----
		    Gateway Software UNIX <-> FIDO
				   
			    Version 3.9.x

----------------------------------------------------------------------

This is FIDOGATE, a gateway software between the worlds of FIDO (and
FTNs, Fido Technology Networks in general) NetMail/EchoMail and the
UNIX mail/news system. FIDOGATE will convert FIDO mail packets to
RFC-style messages and vice versa.

See file doc/fidogate.txt or doc/fidogate.ps for detailed (well, sort
of ... ;-) instructions on how to compile and install FIDOGATE.

There is a mailing list for FIDOGATE discussions and announcements:

    fgate-users@gondor.gun.de

Send mail to

    fgate-users-request@gondor.gun.de

for subscription.



Martin Junius, $Date: 1996/04/17 18:17:32 $
